text: Caria was an ancient region of Asia Minor. Caria may also refer to: *Caria (Moimenta da Beira), a parish in Moimenta da Beira, Portugal *Caria, a parish in Belmonte, Portugal *Caria (butterfly), a genus of metalmark butterflies in the tribe Riodinini == See also == * Carya
title: Caria (disambiguation)
